; Coverage for value.cc line 1802:
; Calling rounded() on a multi-commodity balance goes through the BALANCE
; case in value_t::in_place_round_to_commodity_precision, which dispatches
; to balance_t::in_place_round_to_commodity_precision.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Expenses:Food    10.00 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal Expenses --balance-format "%(rounded(total / 3))\n===\n"
$33.33
3.33 EUR
===
end test
